body.description: 60 Sheets stationary papers 12 scenic watercolor styles writing stationary papers letter, double sided writing paper, 8.5 x 11 inches 12 Watercolor scenic print designs: This colorful stationary paper comes in 12 different styles, 5 sheets in each style. Watercolor landscape painting is colorful and various. You can choose according to your preference. It will add a bright and cheerful atmosphere to your letters and cards Wide range of use: Each writing paper has enough space for you to write and draw freely, you can use it to make party invitation, greeting card, thank you note, etc.. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on June 24, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: Much better than expected and fountain pen friendly!
reviews.reviewText: Lovely paper, very smooth to write on with fountain pen. First sheet I used had slight bleedthrough in places so couldn't use the second side, but that was purely down to a broader nibbed pen laying down more ink. No such issue with the next page written with a finer-nibbed pen, could write on both sides no problem. Really nice designs too. If you're a letter-writer this is good stuff. It's US Letter size 8.5"x11"; I also purchased some JAM branded no. 10 sized envelopes to use with this paper as it's a little bit too wide to fit a standard DL envelope comfortably.
